CustomField.formula:
IF(NOT(ISBLANK(Time_of_Day__c)),

/*THEN strip out the last 8 characters of the Time field as SF time fields still have a date component*/
/* Time fields are stored in SF like: 10:00:00.000Z - so take left 8) */

DATETIMEVALUE(
TEXT(TODAY() + Days_Offset__c) & " " & LEFT(TEXT( Time_of_Day__c),8)
) + 4/24 /* Add 7 hrs during DST to correct GMT time conversion, 7 hrs MST or 8 hrs MDT */
,

/*ELSE use the time of NOW()*/
NOW() + Days_Offset__c + IF(NOT(ISBLANK( Minutes_Offset__c )), (Minutes_Offset__c/60/24) , 0)
)

/********************************************
Need to add 7 hrs to the time because date/time fields convert to GMT -
This needs to be more robust and generic where there is a Time
Zone Pick list on the Campaign
*********************************************/
